0.3.


\(Y\)\(X\)

\[Y_i = \alpha + \beta X_i + \epsilon_i\]

  • \(i\): (individual ID)
  • \(Y_i\): (explained variable)
  • \(X_i\): (explanatory variable)
  • \(\epsilon_i\): (error terms) ; \(E[ \epsilon |X] = 0\)






\[ Y_i = \beta_0 + \beta_1 X_{1i} + \beta_2 X_{2i} + ... + \beta_K X_{Ki} + \epsilon_i \\ = \beta_0 + \pmb{X^{'}} \pmb{\beta} + \epsilon_i \hspace{86pt} \] \[ \begin{align} Y_i &= \beta_0 + \beta_1 X_{1i} + \beta_2 X_{2i} + ... + \beta_K X_{Ki} + \epsilon_i \\ &= \beta_0 + \pmb{X^{'}} \pmb{\beta} + \epsilon_i \end{align} \]

cf. \[ \pmb{X^{'}} \pmb{\beta} = (X_1, X_2, \ldots, X_K) \left ( \begin {array} {ccc} \beta_1 \\ \beta_2 \\ \vdots \\ \beta_K \\ \end {array} \right ) \]

1.3. (omitted variable bias)


(omitted variable bias) \(X\)

  1. \(X\)
  2. \(Y\)

\(Z\)


  • \(Y_i = \alpha + \beta X_i + \gamma Z_i + \epsilon_i\)
  • \(Y_i = \alpha + \beta X_i + \epsilon_i\)


(OLS)

\[\min_{a,b} \sum_{i=i}^{n} (Y_i - a - bX_i) ^2\]

1

\[a: \sum_{i=1}^{n} (Y_i - a - bX_i) = 0\] \[b: \sum_{i=1}^{n} X_i(Y_i - a - bX_i) = 0\]

  • \(a\)

\[a = \tfrac{1}{n} \sum_{i=1}^{n} (Y_i - b X_i) = \bar{Y} - b \bar{X}\]

  • \(b\)

\[ \begin{align} & \sum_{i=1}^{n} X_i (Y_i - \bar{Y} + b \bar{X} - bX_i) = 0 \hspace{73pt} (a)\\ & \sum_{i=1}^{n} (X_i - \bar{X}) (Y_i - \bar{Y}) = b \sum_{i=1}^{n} (X_i - \bar{X}) ^2 \hspace{40pt} (b) \\\\ & b = \frac {\sum_{i=1}^{n} (X_i - \bar{X}) (Y_i - \bar{Y})} {\sum_{i=1}^{n} (X_i - \bar{X}) ^2} = \frac {Cov(X, Y)} {Var(X)} \hspace{28pt} (OLS) \\ \end{align} \]


OLS\(Y\)

\[ \begin{align} b &= \frac {\sum_{i=1}^{n} (X_i - \bar{X_i}) (\alpha + \beta X_i + \gamma Z_i + \epsilon_i - (\alpha + \beta \bar{X_i} + \gamma \bar{Z_i} + \bar{\epsilon_i})) } {\sum_{i=1}^{n} (X_i - \bar{X_i}) ^2} \\\\ &= \frac {\sum_{i=1}^{n} (X_i - \bar{X_i}) [\beta (X_i - \bar{X_i}) + \gamma (Z_i - \bar{Z_i}) + (\epsilon_i - \bar{\epsilon_i})]} {\sum_{i=1}^{n} (X_i - \bar{X_i}) ^2} \\\\ &= \frac {\sum_{i=1}^{n} \beta (X_i - \bar{X_i}) ^2 + \gamma (X_i - \bar{X_i})(Z_i - \bar{Z_i}) + (X_i - \bar{X_i})(\epsilon_i - \bar{\epsilon_i})} {\sum_{i=1}^{n} (X_i - \bar{X_i}) ^2} \\\\ &= \beta + \gamma \frac {\sum_{i=1}^{n} (X_i - \bar{X_i})(Z_i - \bar{Z_i})} {(X_i - \bar{X_i}) ^2} + \frac {\sum_{i=1}^{n} (X_i - \bar{X}) (\epsilon_i - \bar{\epsilon_i})} {\sum_{i=1}^{n} (X_i - \bar{X}) ^2} \hspace{30pt} (E[\epsilon |X] = 0 ) \\\\ &= \beta + \gamma \frac {\sum_{i=1}^{n} (X_i - \bar{X_i})(Z_i - \bar{Z_i})} {(X_i - \bar{X_i}) ^2} \\\\ \end{align} \]

\[ \begin{align} E[\beta |X, Z] &= \beta + \gamma \frac {\sum_{i=1}^{n} (X_i - \bar{X_i})(Z_i - \bar{Z_i})} {(X_i - \bar{X_i}) ^2} \\ &= \beta + \gamma \beta_{XZ} \end{align} \]




  1. OLS2

    1. \(\gamma \neq 0\) \(\) \(Z\)\(Y\)
    2. \(\beta_{XZ} \neq 0\) \(\) \(X\)\(Z\)


  2. \(\gamma\)\(\beta_{XZ}\)

    • \(\gamma > 0\) \(\beta_{XZ} > 0\) \(\gamma \beta_{XZ} > 0\)

      \(Z\)

      • \(\uparrow\) \(\: \Rightarrow \:\) \(\uparrow\) \(\gamma > 0\)
      • \(\uparrow\) \(\: \Rightarrow \:\) \(\uparrow\) \(\beta_{XZ} > 0\)
        \(\therefore\)


  1. RCT\(Z\)
    RCT\(X\) (\(Z\))
    \(\beta_{XZ} = 0\)

\(u_i\)

2 ()

  1. \(u_i^* = \delta_0 + \delta_1 u_1 + e_i\)

    (\(u_i^*\): \(u_i\): )

\[ \begin{align} _i &= \alpha + \beta _i + \gamma Z_i + u^* + \epsilon_i \\ &= \alpha + \beta _i + \gamma Z_i + \delta_0 + \delta_1 u_i + e_i + \epsilon_i \\ &= (\alpha + \delta_0) + \beta _i + \gamma Z_i + \delta_1 u_i + (e_i + \epsilon_i) \\ &= \alpha_0 + \beta _i + \gamma Z_i + \delta_1 u_i + \nu_i \end{align} \]

\(\therefore\) \(\nu_i\)\(u_i\)

\[ \begin{align} & E[e_i + \epsilon_i | X_i, Z_i, u_i] = 0 \\ & E[\nu_i | X_i, Z_i, u_i] = 0 \\ \end{align} \]


(measurement error)


2(\(E[e_i | u_i] = 0\))

  • \(E[e_i | u_i] = 0 \Leftrightarrow Cov(e, u) = 0\)
  • \(u_i\)\(u_i^* = u_i + e_i\)

\[ \begin{align} Cov(e_i, u_i) &= Cov(e_i, u_i^* + e_i) \\ &= Cov(e_i, u_i^*) - Var(e_i) \\ \end{align} \]

\[ Cov(e_i, u_i) = 0 \: \Longrightarrow \: Cov(e_i, u_i^*) = Var(e_i) \]

\(\therefore\)
(\(Cov(e, u) \neq 0\)) (measurement error problem)

\(\beta\)

  • H0\(\beta = 0\)
  • H1\(\beta \neq 0\)


  1. <> () OLS

\[ b_k \sim N(\beta_k, Var(\beta_k)) \: \Longrightarrow \: \frac {b_k - \beta_k} {\sqrt{Var(\beta_k)}} \sim N(0, 1) \]

  1. \(\sigma^2\)\(s^2\)\(s.e.\)

\[ s^2 = \frac {1} {n - (k+1)} \sum_{i=1}^n e_i \: \Longrightarrow \: se(b_k) \simeq \sqrt {\frac {s^2} {\sum_{i=1}^n} (X_i - \bar{X_i}^2 (1 - R_{XZ}^2))} \]

  1. (t)\(n-(k+1)\)t

\[ \frac {b_k - \beta_k} {se(b_k)} \: \sim \: t \: (n - (k + 1)) \]


\[ Y_i = \alpha + \beta X_i + \gamma Z_{1i} + \delta Z_{2i} + \epsilon_i \]

  • 1) (H0: \(\beta = \gamma = \delta = 0\)
  • 2) (H0: \(\gamma = \delta = 0\))
  • 3) (\(\beta + \gamma + \delta = 1\))


(F)F

\[ F = \frac {[SSR_r - SSR_u] / q} {SSR_u / [n - {k + 1}]} \: \sim \: F \: (q, n - (k + 1)) \]

  • \(SSR_r\): (2: \(Y_i = \beta_0 + \epsilon_i\))

  • \(SSR_u\): (2: \(Y_i = \alpha + \beta X_i + \gamma Z_{1i} + \delta Z_{2i} + \epsilon_i\))

  • \(q\):

    • \(SSR_r - SSR_u\)\([n - (k+1-q)] - [n - (k+1)] = q\)

Chow


  • H0: \(\alpha_k = \beta_k\) for all \(k\)

  • H1: \(\alpha_k \neq \beta_k\) for some \(k\)

    • H0: \(Y_i = \alpha_0 + \alpha_1 X_{1i} + \dots + \alpha_K X_{1K} + \epsilon_i\)
    • H1: \(Y_i = \beta_0 + \beta_1 X_{1i} + \dots + \beta_K X_{1K} + \epsilon_i\)
